node.text: Choc chip cookies are really addictive! 👍

A batch of 🍪🍪🍪🍪 satisfy my craving after keep seeing @lebiscuit.id tag me with their irresistible 🍪🍪🍪 🤤🤤🤤
.
.
Joining @homemadeloversss this week Cookies theme #hlfunbake173 with all talented homemade lovers. Only have dark brown colour sugar at home, resulting darker cookies, but the taste sure no doubt super yummy. I really enjoy this giant thick texture 🍪 Crispy on the outside, and soft n chewy on the inside.  Choc chip use #callebaut 811 54% . 
The recipe 👉 from @joshuaweissman Youtube channel “Recreating Levain 🍪cookies” Bake 1/2 recipe, sugar combination 220g. .
.
Hope everyone staying safe and happy.
.
